skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: zero excuses fitness
des:
Listen to the latest blogs posts from 0 Excuses Fitness. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. You can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next episodes by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next".
